  "description": "FHIR types + profile classes generated via @atomic-ehr/codegen — v1 catalog: R4 core, US Core 6.1/9.0, CARIN BB 2.2.0, PDex 2.2.0, HRex 1.1.0, C4DIC 1.1.0, PAS 2.1.0.",
